### ============================================================
### HealthConnector Prior Authorization Platform — API Tests
### Use with IntelliJ HTTP Client or VS Code REST Client plugin
### ============================================================
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### After login, copy the accessToken below:
@adminToken = PASTE_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
@providerToken = PASTE_PROVIDER_TOKEN_HERE
@payerToken = PASTE_PAYER_TOKEN_HERE

### After creating, paste IDs here:
@providerId = PASTE_PROVIDER_ID_HERE
@payerId = PASTE_PAYER_ID_HERE
@authorizationId = PASTE_AUTHORIZATION_ID_HERE
@notificationId = PASTE_NOTIFICATION_ID_HERE

### ============================================================
### 1. AUTHENTICATION
### ============================================================

### 1.1 Login as Super Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@healthconnector.com",
  "password": "Admin@1234"
}

---

### 1.2 Login as Provider (after creating one)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "provider@hospital.com",
  "password": "PASTE_TEMP_PASSWORD_FROM_EMAIL"
}

---

### 1.3 Login as Payer (after creating one)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "payer@insurance.com",
  "password": "PASTE_TEMP_PASSWORD_FROM_EMAIL"
}

---

### 1.4 Refresh Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json
Refresh-Token: PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE

---

### 1.5 Change Password (authenticated user)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/change-password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "currentPassword": "Admin@1234",
  "newPassword": "NewAdmin@5678",
  "confirmPassword": "NewAdmin@5678"
}

---

### 1.6 Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---

### ============================================================
### 2. PROVIDER MANAGEMENT (SUPER_ADMIN only)
### ============================================================

### 2.1 Create Provider
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/providers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "firstName": "Dr. John",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "email": "provider@hospital.com",
  "mobile": "+14155552671",
  "organizationName": "City General Hospital",
  "npi": "1234567893",
  "address": "100 Medical Drive, San Francisco, CA 94102"
}

---

### 2.2 List All Providers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/providers?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---

### 2.3 Get Provider by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/providers/{{providerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---

### 2.4 Block Provider
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/providers/{{providerId}}/block
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---

### 2.5 Activate Provider
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/providers/{{providerId}}/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---

### 2.6 Reset Provider Password
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/providers/{{providerId}}/reset-password
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---

### 2.7 Delete Provider (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/providers/{{providerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---

### ============================================================
### 3. PAYER MANAGEMENT (SUPER_ADMIN only)
### ============================================================

### 3.1 Create Payer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Johnson",
  "email": "payer@insurance.com",
  "mobile": "+14155559001",
  "organizationName": "BlueCross Insurance Co.",
  "address": "200 Insurance Ave, Chicago, IL 60601"
}

---

### 3.2 List All Payers (Admin or Provider)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payers?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---

### 3.3 Get Payer by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payers/{{payerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---

### 3.4 Block Payer
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/payers/{{payerId}}/block
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---

### 3.5 Activate Payer
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/payers/{{payerId}}/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---

### 3.6 Reset Payer Password
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payers/{{payerId}}/reset-password
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---

### ============================================================
### 4. PRIOR AUTHORIZATION — PROVIDER FLOW
### ============================================================

### 4.1 Create Authorization Draft (PROVIDER)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/authorizations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{providerToken}}

{
  "payerId": "{{payerId}}",
  "patientName": "Jane Doe",
  "patientDateOfBirth": "1985-06-15",
  "patientAddress": "456 Oak Street, Austin, TX 78701",
  "patientMobile": "+15125559234",
  "insuranceNumber": "INS-2026-78901",
  "memberId": "MEM-2026-12345",
  "primaryDiagnosisCode": "J18.9",
  "diagnosisDescription": "Pneumonia, unspecified organism",
  "procedureCode": "99213",
  "procedureDescription": "Office visit, established patient, moderate complexity",
  "clinicalNotes": "Patient presents with 5-day fever, productive cough, and dyspnea. Chest X-ray confirms bilateral infiltrates. IV antibiotics recommended.",
  "requestedServiceDate": "2026-07-01",
  "priority": "URGENT",
  "placeOfService": "INPATIENT"
}

---

### 4.2 Get My Authorizations (PROVIDER)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/authorizations/my?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{providerToken}}

---

### 4.3 Get Authorization by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/authorizations/{{authorizationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{providerToken}}

---

### 4.4 Trigger AI Review (PROVIDER)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/authorizations/{{authorizationId}}/ai-review
Authorization: Bearer {{providerToken}}

---

### 4.5 Submit Authorization to Payer (PROVIDER)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/authorizations/{{authorizationId}}/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{providerToken}}

---

### 4.6 Delete Draft Authorization (PROVIDER)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/authorizations/{{authorizationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{providerToken}}

---

### ============================================================
### 5. PRIOR AUTHORIZATION — PAYER REVIEW FLOW
### ============================================================

### 5.1 Get Payer Queue (PAYER)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/authorizations/queue?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{payerToken}}

---

### 5.2 Approve Authorization (PAYER)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/authorizations/{{authorizationId}}/approve?notes=Medically+necessary,+approved+for+7+days
Authorization: Bearer {{payerToken}}

---

### 5.3 Reject Authorization (PAYER)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/authorizations/{{authorizationId}}/reject?reason=Diagnosis+does+not+meet+criteria+for+inpatient+admission
Authorization: Bearer {{payerToken}}

---

### 5.4 Request More Info (PAYER)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/authorizations/{{authorizationId}}/request-info?notes=Please+provide+prior+treatment+history+and+lab+results
Authorization: Bearer {{payerToken}}

---

### ============================================================
### 6. ADMIN — ALL AUTHORIZATIONS
### ============================================================

### 6.1 Get All Authorizations (SUPER_ADMIN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/authorizations?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---

### ============================================================
### 7. CHAT — PROVIDER ↔ PAYER MESSAGING
### ============================================================

### 7.1 Send Message (PROVIDER to PAYER)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/authorizations/{{authorizationId}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{providerToken}}

{
  "content": "Hi, I have attached additional lab results supporting the inpatient admission. Please review at your earliest convenience."
}

---

### 7.2 Send Message (PAYER to PROVIDER)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/authorizations/{{authorizationId}}/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{payerToken}}

{
  "content": "Thank you. We have received the lab results and will complete our review within 24 hours."
}

---

### 7.3 Get Messages for Authorization
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/authorizations/{{authorizationId}}/messages?page=0&size=50
Authorization: Bearer {{providerToken}}

---

### ============================================================
### 8. NOTIFICATIONS
### ============================================================

### 8.1 Get My Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{providerToken}}

---

### 8.2 Get Unread Notification Count
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{providerToken}}

---

### 8.3 Mark Notification as Read
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/{{notificationId}}/read
Authorization: Bearer {{providerToken}}

---

### 8.4 Mark All Notifications as Read
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{providerToken}}

---

### ============================================================
### 9. AUDIT LOGS (SUPER_ADMIN only)
### ============================================================

### 9.1 Get All Audit Logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit-logs?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---

### 9.2 Get Audit Logs for a User
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit-logs/user/{{providerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---

### 9.3 Get Audit Logs for an Entity
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/audit-logs/entity/AUTHORIZATION/{{authorizationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---

### ============================================================
### 10. ANALYTICS / DASHBOARDS
### ============================================================

### 10.1 Admin Dashboard (SUPER_ADMIN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---

### 10.2 Provider Dashboard (PROVIDER)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics/provider/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{providerToken}}

---

### 10.3 Payer Dashboard (PAYER)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics/payer/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{payerToken}}

---

### ============================================================
### 11. SYSTEM CONFIGURATION (SUPER_ADMIN only)
### ============================================================

### 11.1 Get System Config
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/system/config
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

---

### 11.2 Update System Config
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/system/config
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "geminiModel": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite",
  "geminiTemperature": 0.3,
  "geminiMaxTokens": 4096,
  "geminiEnabled": true,
  "aiReviewRequiredBeforeSubmit": false,
  "fhirEnabled": true,
  "maxFailedAttempts": 5,
  "passwordExpiryDays": 90
}

---

### ============================================================
### 12. HEALTH CHECK & SWAGGER
### ============================================================

### 12.1 Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health

---

### 12.2 Swagger UI
GET {{baseUrl}}/swagger-ui.html

---

### 12.3 API Docs (JSON)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api-docs

---
